        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari <lb n="2"/>divi Nervae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Ner<lb break="no" n="3"/>vae Traiano <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Ger</abbr><ex>manico</ex></expan> Dacico <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> X&amp;lt;V<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>&amp;gt;III <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> VI co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>VI <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> optumo <lb n="8"/>maxsumoque <note>sic</note> <lb n="9"/>principi Nesca<lb break="no" n="10"/>nienses <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten ist nur der Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Mehrere Buchstaben nur handschriftlich überliefert. Datierung: Die Angaben in der Inschrift stimmen chronologisch nicht überein: trib.pot XIII (10. 12. 108 - 9. 12. 109), imp. VI (Herbst 106 - August/September 114), cos. VI (112-117); am ehesten ist wohl die Zahl der trib. pot. in XVIII (10. 12. 113 - 9. 12. 114) zu ändern.</p>
            </div>
